00:01:21.520 --> 00:01:22.760
So let's talk about clickbaiting,

00:01:22.860 --> 00:01:25.200
some of you had accused me
on becoming a clickbaiter.

00:01:25.300 --> 00:01:26.200
Let's talk about what that means.

00:01:26.320 --> 00:01:27.000
So... [chuckles]

00:01:27.100 --> 00:01:30.060
To actually clickbait,
like real genuine clickbait,

00:01:30.160 --> 00:01:33.800
is when you put up an advertisement
or a thumbnail or a description,

00:01:33.900 --> 00:01:36.200
that has absolutely nothing to do
with the video, at all.

00:01:36.300 --> 00:01:38.400
Just absolutely unrelated
whatsoever, you know.

00:01:38.500 --> 00:01:39.800
That's clickbait.

00:01:39.900 --> 00:01:41.400
Now if you take a thumbnail,

00:01:41.500 --> 00:01:44.000
and you dress it up a little bit
and you make it look more attractive.

00:01:44.100 --> 00:01:46.300
And if you change the title to be enticing,

00:01:46.400 --> 00:01:47.800
and make you want to click,

00:01:47.940 --> 00:01:49.000
that's called marketing!

00:01:49.100 --> 00:01:50.400
That's called selling, guys.

00:01:50.500 --> 00:01:51.800
- I mean--
- Which is what you want,

00:01:51.900 --> 00:01:55.460
because you want to click on something
that you have a desire to click on.

00:01:55.560 --> 00:01:56.740
I mean, if you're going to buy a house

00:01:56.840 --> 00:01:58.540
and somebody painted the house
to make it look nicer,

00:01:58.580 --> 00:02:00.200
would you accuse them of clickbaiting?

00:02:00.380 --> 00:02:03.100
Because they're like, enticing you
to buy this house, making it better--

00:02:03.260 --> 00:02:04.900
Making it seem better than it actually is?

00:02:05.040 --> 00:02:07.000
Uh that's just-- that's good
old fashioned marketing guys,

00:02:07.120 --> 00:02:09.180
and I've learned that
by watching other channels

00:02:09.220 --> 00:02:11.800
I mean, doing the collaborations in L.A.,
there's a lot of creators

00:02:11.900 --> 00:02:14.320
who put a lot of work
into their thumbnails...

00:02:14.840 --> 00:02:16.400
that make them more clickable.

00:02:16.500 --> 00:02:17.380
And that's what I'm going for.

00:02:17.500 --> 00:02:20.900
I'm not going for clickbaiting,
I'm making my thumbnails more clickable.

00:02:21.000 --> 00:02:22.200
So I hope you can appreciate that.

00:02:22.380 --> 00:02:24.900
Because that's an added expense,
it's added time,

00:02:25.000 --> 00:02:26.500
and it's something
I'm trying to do for you.

00:02:26.600 --> 00:02:30.000
You always find good content in my videos
and you'll always find the thumbnails

00:02:30.100 --> 00:02:32.400
and the titles related
to the content in the video.

00:02:32.500 --> 00:02:34.400
Unless you're gonna sign up
for YouTube Red,

00:02:34.500 --> 00:02:37.860
or you're going to, like, privately fund
The King of Random foundation

00:02:37.860 --> 00:02:40.900
or something of that nature, um,
you're getting these videos for free.

00:02:41.100 --> 00:02:42.900
And there's no such thing as free.

00:02:43.000 --> 00:02:44.200
Somebody's paying for them

00:02:44.340 --> 00:02:47.000
and that's the businesses
who are advertising with Google.

00:02:47.140 --> 00:02:48.100
That's how you're paying so...

00:02:48.220 --> 00:02:52.600
But ultimately, too, our service to you is
to create good quality content for free.

00:02:52.700 --> 00:02:54.500
- That's our purpose.
- That's right.

00:02:54.700 --> 00:02:56.300
So click-- click on those videos.

00:02:56.400 --> 00:02:59.100
I guess that's all we have to say,
click on the videos, click on the videos!

00:02:59.200 --> 00:03:01.900
I mean, your numbers,
your responses to the videos tell us

00:03:02.120 --> 00:03:03.420
if we're doing better or worse.

00:03:03.500 --> 00:03:05.400
If we put time and work
into our thumbnails

00:03:05.500 --> 00:03:07.500
and you click more on them,
then obviously,

00:03:07.600 --> 00:03:09.100
that's working,
we're gonna do more of it.

00:03:09.200 --> 00:03:10.600
It's not clickbait, it's just marketing.

00:03:10.700 --> 00:03:12.640
And the more you guys
actually click on these videos,

00:03:12.740 --> 00:03:15.220
the more support it gives to us,
to have a team

00:03:15.340 --> 00:03:16.900
- to bring more content to you.
- Exactly.

00:03:17.000 --> 00:03:18.200
So it's really a win-win.

00:03:18.400 --> 00:03:20.460
And that brings up another point here,

00:03:20.460 --> 00:03:21.760
I want to talk about AdBlockers.

00:03:21.860 --> 00:03:24.264
Some of you are very proud
about using AdBlockers.

00:03:24.340 --> 00:03:26.400
