The thing you got to realize, is when you
start posting videos on YouTube,

00:15:05.780 --> 00:15:07.960
even if they're
excellent excellent videos...

00:15:08.460 --> 00:15:09.480
nobody's going to watch them.

00:15:09.480 --> 00:15:11.180
Because there's so much content on YouTube,

00:15:11.180 --> 00:15:12.860
there needs to be some way to stand out so I was...

00:15:13.120 --> 00:15:15.000
I was putting a lot of time into making videos

00:15:15.260 --> 00:15:18.000
and getting 100, 200 views.

00:15:18.320 --> 00:15:20.500
So I had to get creative and find
other ways to market myself,

00:15:20.500 --> 00:15:24.720
I started writing articles for websites,
I started posting, uh, weekly...

00:15:24.980 --> 00:15:27.460
how-to step by steps on different, uh, websites

00:15:27.460 --> 00:15:29.300
that would eventually feature me on the front page

00:15:29.540 --> 00:15:31.020
and that would
drive a little more traffic.

